narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: You have to work but you will learn the language well enough to have a conversation in a month and even better in a semester. It's definitely worth it if you want to start learning Italian.
Introduces you to the basics of italian in a fun way...you will leave the class being able to communicate in italian
I would definitely tell them to take the class because it's very laid back, yet you will learn the material.
Italian was a hard course, just due to the fast-pace of the curriculum. However, you will definitely have a great base of the language if you do choose to take the course.
